 There exist many tools you can use to extract various bits of preliminary information from your running JVM.
JPS :- Will list out each and every JVM process running on your machine, along with each process’ PID .
jmap –histo:live 45417 :- jmap will make a complete dump of the application’s heap memory for prcess PID = 45417.
VisualVM :- 
BTrace :-
